CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 30, 1946, pg. 17, reads: "Art Exhibit - The 'John Brown Art Series,' on display at the Centre Avenue YMCA, created unusual attention in art circles here. Jacob Lawrence, the artist, explains the various paintings to Mrs. Dorothy Sadar and Armando del Cimmuto.-Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Dorothy Sadar and Armando del Cimmuto standing on either side of artist Jacob Lawrence, pointing to picture in his "John Brown Art Series," in Centre Avenue YMCA
